                                    | till the end of the examination
                                li The candidate has been temporarily given admission for the examination, assuming that all
                                    | the information in the application form is correct. If at any stage the information filled 
                                    | by the candidates is found to be incorrect or false, the candidate will be canceled and the 
                                    | candidate himself responsible for the result. 
